summary:
Bachelor’s degree in English Education with three years experience teaching primary school English, General Studies and Computer. A self-starter and quick learner. Recognized skills in time management and team management. Excellent in written and oral skills in both English and Chinese.

Currently living in Haarlem and looking for any English-speaking job opportunities in the Netherlands.
